MTF,<br><br>
How dare you insult your feathered friends!<br><br>
Chickens are intelligent, warm, and caring.<br><br>
Chickens are nice and feathery.<br><br>
Chickens talk.<br><br>
I hereby lodge a class action PROTEST against your use of chickens in the same post as the likes of the extict pre-cambrian life form. That's well befor trilobites! And don't pick on monotremes, either! <br><br>
A better selection to use on the same post could be any of the following less discriminatory life forms: tick, leech, clamydia, fungus, may apple, skunk cabbage, protozoa, tapeworm, nematode, crotch rot, flea, plague, maggot, horn worm catapiller, mange mite, ear mite abcess, staphlococcus, slime mold, eye worm, trichinosis, pus, fistulae, abcess, hemarhoid, and all the rest of the better descriptive stuff.<br><br>
Get the message!<br><br>
Big Bird
